cg.el -- a major mode for editing Constraint Grammar files

See http://beta.visl.sdu.dk/constraint_grammar.html for what
Constraint Grammar is.

Currently does syntax highlighting (based on sh-mode) and some simple
indentation.

There is also another Emacs mode named cg-mode:
http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/CgMode


